                  <summary/>
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4618Prayer">Protective prayer against any known or unknown disease</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ሰብእ፡ ዘይትዓወቅ፡ ወዘዒይትአወቅ፡ 
                        አቢ፡ አቢ፡ አቢ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note>The prayer is preceded by a figure consisting of nine squares, five being human faces and three being eyes.</note>
                  </msItem> 
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4619Prayer">Protective prayer against Bāryā and Lagewon</title>
                     <!-- Cp also LIT4575MagicPr with a partly different incipit -->
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ባርያ፡ ወለጌዎን፡ ርኩስ፡ ዘይሰልብ፡ ልበ፡ 
                        ሰብእ፡ ወያጸልም፡ አዕይንተ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note>Cp. <bibl>
                           <ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><citedRange>88</citedRange>
                        </bibl>.
                     </note>
                   </msItem>  
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4620Prayer">Protective prayer against the diseases of the smiths and the demons</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ነሀብት፡ ወአጋንንት፡ አላሁማ፡ ወያኑራ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note>The prayer is followed by a figure consisting of a cross with a human face and eight eyes.</note>
                  </msItem>       
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4621Prayer">Protective prayer to chase demons away</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በዘያርኅቆሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ ወይሰድዶሙ፡ ለሰይጣናት፡ 
                        እምላዕለ፡ ሰብእ፡ ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ 
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ኦአምላከ፡ ፋኑኤል፡ አድኅና፡ እምአጋንንት፡ እኩያን፡ ወእምሰብእ፡ መሠርያን፡ <choice><sic>ለአማትከ፡</sic></choice> ወለተ፡ ሥላሴ።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner, <persName ref="PRS11558WalattaS">Walatta Śǝllāse</persName>, is written in the supplication formula 
                     at the end of the prayer.</note>
                     <listBibl type="editions">
                        <bibl>
                           <ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><citedRange>113f.</citedRange>
                        </bibl>
                     </listBibl>
                     <listBibl type="translation" xml:lang="de">
                        <bibl>
                           <ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><citedRange>113f.</citedRange>
                        </bibl>
                     </listBibl>
                  </msItem>       
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4622Prayer">Protective prayer against colic</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ 
                        <choice><sic>ቍርፀት፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ቍርጠት፡</corr></choice> ዘተፈነወ፡ እምኀበ፡ ወልድ፡ ዋሕድ፡ ከመ፡ ይርዳእ፡ 
                        ወይቤዙ፡ ውሉደ፡ እጓለ፡ እመሕያው፡ ሸገር፡ ሸገር፡ ሸገር፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note></note>
                  </msItem>       
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4623Prayer">Protective prayer against colic</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ 
                        <choice><sic>ቍርፀት፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ቍርጠት፡</corr></choice> በከፓኮስ፡ ስምከ፡ በኄርያኖስ፡ ስምከ፡ በዳፌል፡ 
                        ስምከ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note>The prayer is followed by figures with squares and triangles.</note>
                  </msItem>       
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4624Prayer">Protective prayer ayer against the pain</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ 
                        <choice><sic>ውግዓት፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ውጋት፡</corr></choice> ምድምያስ፡ ምድምያስ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note></note>
                  </msItem>       
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4625Prayer">Protective prayer against the pain</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ውጋት፡</supplied> ሰላም፡ ለገቦከ፡ ኵናተ፡ <choice><sic>ለጊጊሮስ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ለንጊኖስ፡</corr></choice> 
                        ዘወግዖ፡
                     </incipit>
                        <note>Cp. <bibl>
                           <ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><citedRange>96 n. 3</citedRange>
                        </bibl>.
                        </note>
                  </msItem>  
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4626Prayer">Protective prayer against the spell</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ዓይነት፡ የአብ፡ ስሙ፡ አብ፡ ሸልሸልሸል፡ የወልድ፡ ስም፡ ሐፍሸልሸል፡ የመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ስም፡ ጠብሸልሸል፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note>The prayer is followed by a figure consisting of squares divided by diagonal lines and circles.</note>
                  </msItem>       
